data.text:
If you'd like to order a photo strip, choose the 4x8 photo print size and ignore the initial crop option. Once you are in the cart to check out choose the crop option "none" to print the entire strip.

Any photo strip printed will have white strips to the side of the strip. Please keep this in mind when ordering larger sizes or keepsakes.
